entries.s_10: Ah, finally. Thanks for helping gather the supplies. I know it wasn't easy. Here, take this. I hope you find it useful in your adventures.
entries.s_11: We're still good here. We don't need any of your heroics today.
entries.s_13: No problem. I'll be sure to let Rydel know of your good deed.
entries.s_14: Are you here to help us with the supplies?
entries.s_18: Ah, yes. Good ol' Rydel. Well, glad you're here. Get in there, and get those supplies back. We need them!
entries.s_22: Good. You there! Get back to work!
entries.s_24: Citizen, move along. We're transferring precious cargo here. Nothing to be concerned about.
entries.s_9: Look, we need those supplies as soon as possible! Get going!
